  "description": "Erection of basement excavation and extension with&nbsp;lightwell to rear (no. 49); ground floor rear extensions with two skylights and one roof lantern; full-width\r\nrear dormers; front dormer (no.49) and rooflights to the front roof slope.&nbsp;",
